  "elapsed_s": 2.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Well, I said to Wanda, for better or for worse, we have to-- [?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Teresa-- ?] get [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Teresa ?] out of there because-- always remembering my mother's admonition-- we should try to be together and survive together.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I went to the convent.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I spoke, spoke with Mother Superior.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I asked her if I could visit with [?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Teresa. ?] I said, I was passing by, and I had a little something for her.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I took a bundle with me of civilian clothes because [?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Teresa ?] wore a brown habit while she was in the convent.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And when I saw [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Teresa, ?] I said, well, let's take a little walk.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And while we were walking, I said, [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Teresa, ?] we are walking straight into the exit.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we are leaving.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And she was a little nonplussed over it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I explained to her that it's very dangerous to remain in Warsaw, [SIGHS] that we must leave, that we are not sure what we are going to do, but this is not the place for us to stay.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And she said, OK, whatever you say.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we came up to Wanda's place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we-- sure enough, we got there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the bombs started falling.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we had to run into the basement to hide from the bombs.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then we realized for sure that we have to leave Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Can you tell me what it was like while you were still working in the factory, the atmosphere of the Germans, with what was going on?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Did you hear stories?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm glad you asked the question because I, I would have wanted to address it myself.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
